.OmissionReason.deep","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.OmissionReason.deep\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">OmissionReason</span>.<span class=\"name\">deep</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.OmissionReason\">OmissionReason</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L329-L333","name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.OmissionReason","line":329,"kind":"inductive","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.OmissionReason","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">inductive</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.OmissionReason\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">OmissionReason</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L317-L327","name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.withBindingBodyUnusedName","line":317,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.withBindingBodyUnusedName","doc":"Enters the body of the current expression, which must be a lambda or forall.\nThe binding variable is passed to `d` as `Syntax`, and it is an identifier that has been annotated with the fvar expression\nfor the variable.\n\nIf `preserveName` is `false` (the default), gives the binder an unused name.\nOtherwise, it tries to preserve the textual form of the name, preserving whether it is hygienic.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.withBindingBodyUnusedName\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">withBindingBodyUnusedName</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">d</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Syntax\">Syntax</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM\">DelabM</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">preserveName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool.false\">false</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM\">DelabM</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L308-L315","name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.mkAnnotatedIdent","line":308,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.mkAnnotatedIdent","doc":"Creates an identifier that is annotated with the term `e`, using a fresh position using the `HoleIterator`.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.mkAnnotatedIdent\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkAnnotatedIdent</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM\">DelabM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Meta.html#Lean.Syntax.Ident\">Ident</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L274-L306","name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.getUnusedName","line":274,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.getUnusedName","doc":"Gets an name based on `suggestion` that is unused in the local context.\nErases macro scopes.\nIf `pp.safeShadowing` is true, then the name is allowed to shadow a name in the local context\nif the name does not appear in `body`.\n\nIf `preserveName` is false, then returns the name, possibly with fresh macro scopes added.\nIf `suggestion` has macro scopes then the result does as well.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.getUnusedName\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">getUnusedName</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">suggestion</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">body</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">preserveName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool.false\">false</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM\">DelabM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L267-L272","name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.withAnnotateTermInfoUnlessAnnotated","line":267,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.withAnnotateTermInfoUnlessAnnotated","doc":"Modifies the delaborator so that it ensures resulting term is annotated using `annotateTermInfoUnlessAnnotated`.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.withAnnotateTermInfoUnlessAnnotated\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">withAnnotateTermInfoUnlessAnnotated</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">d</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.Delab\">Delab</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.Delab\">Delab</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L260-L265","name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.withAnnotateTermInfo","line":260,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.withAnnotateTermInfo","doc":"Modifies the delaborator so that it annotates the resulting term using `annotateTermInfo`.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.withAnnotateTermInfo\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">withAnnotateTermInfo</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">d</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.Delab\">Delab</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.Delab\">Delab</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L249-L258","name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.annotateTermInfoUnlessAnnotated","line":249,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.annotateTermInfoUnlessAnnotated","doc":"Annotates the term with the current expression position and registers `TermInfo`\nto associate the term to the current expression, unless the syntax has a synthetic position\nand associated `Info` already.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.annotateTermInfoUnlessAnnotated\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">annotateTermInfoUnlessAnnotated</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">stx</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Meta.html#Lean.Syntax.Term\">Term</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.Delab\">Delab</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L240-L247","name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.annotateTermInfo","line":240,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.annotateTermInfo","doc":"Annotates the term with the current expression position and registers `TermInfo`\nto associate the term to the current expression.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.annotateTermInfo\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">annotateTermInfo</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">stx</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Meta.html#Lean.Syntax.Term\">Term</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a 