ption</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">opt</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/Options.html#Lean.Options\">Options</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">d</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.Delab\">Delab</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.Delab\">Delab</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L178-L180","name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.getPPOption","line":178,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.getPPOption","doc":"Evaluate option accessor, using subterm-specific options if set. "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.getPPOption\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">getPPOption</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">opt</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/Options.html#Lean.Options\">Options</a> → <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM\">DelabM</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L170-L176","name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.getOptionsAtCurrPos","line":170,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.getOptionsAtCurrPos","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.getOptionsAtCurrPos\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">getOptionsAtCurrPos</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM\">DelabM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Data/Options.html#Lean.Options\">Options</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L148-L168","name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.getExprKind","line":148,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.getExprKind","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.getExprKind\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">getExprKind</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM\">DelabM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L142-L146","name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.attrApp_delab_","line":142,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.attrApp_delab_","doc":"`@[app_delab c]` registers a delaborator for applications with head constant `c`.\nSuch delaborators also apply to the constant `c` itself (known as a \"nullary application\").\n\nThis attribute should be applied to definitions of type `Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.Delab`.\n\nWhen defining delaborators for constant applications, one should prefer this attribute over `@[delab app.c]`,\nas `@[app_delab c]` first performs name resolution on `c` in the current scope.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.attrApp_delab_\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">attrApp_delab_</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.ParserDescr\">ParserDescr</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L107-L131","name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.delabAttribute","line":107,"kind":"opaque","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.delabAttribute","doc":"Registers a delaborator.\n\n`@[delab k]` registers a declaration of type `Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.Delab` for the\n`Lean.Expr` constructor `k`. Multiple delaborators for a single constructor are tried in turn until\nthe first success. If the term to be delaborated is an application of a constant `c`, elaborators\nfor `app.c` are tried first; this is also done for `Expr.const`s (\"nullary applications\") to reduce\nspecial casing. If the term is an `Expr.mdata` with a single key `k`, `mdata.k` is tried first.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.delabAttribute\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">delabAttribute</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/KeyedDeclsAttribute.html#Lean.KeyedDeclsAttribute\">KeyedDeclsAttribute</a> <a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.Delab\">Delab</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L101-L105","name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.instMonadQuotationDelabM","line":101,"kind":"instance","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.instMonadQuotationDelabM","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.instMonadQuotationDelabM\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">instMonadQuotationDelabM</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.MonadQuotation\">MonadQuotation</a> <a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.htm